v class=\"markdown-heading\" dir=\"auto\"\u003e\u003ch1 tabindex=\"-1\" class=\"heading-element\" dir=\"auto\"\u003eBGC pipeline project\u003c/h1\u003e\u003ca id=\"user-content-bgc-pipeline-project\" class=\"anchor\" aria-label=\"Permalink: BGC pipeline project\" href=\"#bgc-pipeline-project\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"octicon octicon-link\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003cpath d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"auto\"\u003eThis project focuses on the development of a bioinformatics pipeline for the analysis of Biosynthetic Gene Clusters (BGCs), with an emphasis on identifying and associating them with antimicrobial potential.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"auto\"\u003eThe pipeline integrates the following tools:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul dir=\"auto\"\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eantiSMASH (\u003ca href=\"https://github.com/antismash\"\u003ehttps://github.com/antismash\u003c/a\u003e);\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eBIG-SCAPE (\u003ca href=\"https://github.com/medema-group/BiG-SCAPE\"\u003ehttps://github.com/medema-group/BiG-SCAPE\u003c/a\u003e);\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePOEM-pipeline (\u003ca href=\"https://github.com/Rinoahu/POEM_py3k\"\u003ehttps://github.com/Rinoahu/POEM_py3k\u003c/a\u003e);\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDeepSEA (\u003ca href=\"https://github.com/tiagocabralborelli/DeepSEA-code\"\u003ehttps://github.com/tiagocabralborelli/DeepSEA-code\u003c/a\u003e);\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eKOfam (\u003ca href=\"https://github.com/takaram/kofam_scan\"\u003ehttps://github.com/takaram/kofam_scan\u003c/a\u003e);\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDIAMOND (\u003ca href=\"https://github.com/bbuchfink/diamond\"\u003ehttps://github.com/bbuchfink/diamond\u003c/a\u003e);\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"auto\"\u003eBelow is the current pipeline workflow.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ca target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://private-user-images.githubusercontent.com/180195660/572150467-21624153-c440-4f36-a2ad-7c9b2e3f0ecf.png?jwt=eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJpc3MiOiJnaXRodWIuY29tIiwiYXVkIjoicmF3LmdpdGh1YnVzZXJjb250ZW50LmNvbSIsImtleSI6ImtleTUiLCJleHAiOjE3NzQ5OTEyODgsIm5iZiI6MTc3NDk5MDk4OCwicGF0aCI6Ii8xODAxOTU2NjAvNTcyMTUwNDY3LTIxNjI0MTUzLWM0NDAtNGYzNi1hMmFkLTdjOWIyZTNmMGVjZi5wbmc_.pwD7cHlQWNP54MZSEBjm9FpenTLUEjVWV9KW-zJGHbI\"\u003e\u003cimg width=\"2000\" height=\"2000\" alt=\"Imagem meu github\" src=\"https://private-user-images.githubusercontent.com/180195660/572150467-21624153-c440-4f36-a2ad-7c9b2e3f0ecf.png?jwt=eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJpc3MiOiJnaXRodWIuY29tIiwiYXVkIjoicmF3LmdpdGh1YnVzZXJjb250ZW50LmNvbSIsImtleSI6ImtleTUiLCJleHAiOjE3NzQ5OTEyODgsIm5iZiI6MTc3NDk5MDk4OCwicGF0aCI6Ii8xODAxOTU2NjAvNTcyMTUwNDY3LTIxNjI0MTUzLWM0NDAtNGYzNi1hMmFkLTdjOWIyZTNmMGVjZi5wbmc_.pwD7cHlQWNP54MZSEBjm9FpenTLUEjVWV9KW-zJGHbI\" style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto; max-height: 2000px;\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"markdown-heading\" dir=\"auto\"\u003e\u003ch2 tabindex=\"-1\" class=\"heading-element\" dir=\"auto\"\u003eInstallation\u003c/h2\u003e\u003ca id=\"user-content-installation\" class=\"anchor\" aria-label=\"Permalink: Installation\" href=\"#installation\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"octicon octicon-link\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003cpath d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.